abstract: Her sister gets more press, but Susan Wojcicki has plenty of interesting ties to Google as well.
snippet: Her sister gets more press, but Susan Wojcicki has plenty of interesting ties to Google as well.
lead_paragraph: Susan Wojcicki is getting a little more attention after her sister Anne was in the limelight. It must have felt a little like being Jan Brady, after all, her sister married Google’s billionaire co-founder Sergey Brin.
